    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Play test games:</span> After learning a batch of words, play 2-3 practice games specifically trying to use them. Active deployment cements vocabulary far better than passive reading.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
